suppose we have a huge data but we want to see top 3 data only

syntax
select col1, col2 ,col3 from table_name where condition Limit 3;

ex: 
select * from table_name Limit 3;

ex: 
select * from table_name where name="Raj" Limit 3;
 

ex : 
select * from table_name limit 3,3;
//skip first 3 record then show next 3 record

